---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Eco-Friendly Decorating in Middlesex | Hancock' description='Professional eco-friendly decorating across Middlesex and the Home Counties. Fixed-price quotes, City & Guilds certified, no subcontractors.' activePage='services'>
<section style="position:relative;height:400px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(1).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 30%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 56px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/services" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Services</a> / Eco-Friendly Decorating</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,56px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Eco-Friendly Decorating</h1>
    <p style="font-size:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;max-width:500px;line-height:1.5;">Low-VOC and natural paint systems. Minimal chemical exposure without compromising on quality.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:72px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">What this means in practice</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,34px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 24px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Modern eco paints are now comparable to conventional alternatives.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 20px;">Low-VOC (volatile organic compound) paints have improved substantially. The coverage, durability, and washability of quality eco paint systems are now comparable to conventional alternatives — and the chemical off-gassing during and after application is significantly lower. For households with children, allergy sufferers, or clients who spend a lot of time in freshly decorated spaces, this matters.</p>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 20px;">We use Farrow &amp; Ball, Little Greene, and Earthborn among others — brands with full-range low-VOC or zero-VOC options across emulsion, eggshell, and gloss finishes. These aren't inferior products; they're the premium choice in most cases.</p>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">If you want eco-specified decorating, just tell us when you enquire. We'll specify the system and quote accordingly.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:64px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,40px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 16px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;">Get an eco decorating quote.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 36px;">Low-VOC systems specified and priced clearly.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:07734903439" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">07734 903439</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
